Summary: 5 orange pulsating lights hovering over Lake of the Ozarks
divs: sighting detailsat approx. 9:45pm as i was sitting on my deck and i saw very large orange pulsating lights. they were rectangular shaped and there were 5 of them as i recall. i only saw them for 5-10 sec. before they simply went out. there was no noise at all and since i had lights on behind me i was unable to tell if there was any type of vehicle. i didn't have time to get any pictures. i recently spoke with another woman who saw something the same night. she said what she saw was out of "close encounters of the third kind" a large disc shaped object with beams of light coming from the bottom. she said this happened at about 8:30pm 8\15\2011. i called the local sheriff's office and they said they didn't have any reports of strange lights.
